  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5439303/" class="title-link">刚刚瞄了眼一篇关于此书的论文</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5439303"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1430341/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1430341-12.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1430341/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">三一</span>
